{"tid":764419,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"東京居酒屋生啤按顧客態度收費 呼喝侍應收貴逾兩倍","createTime":"2018-08-02T03:32:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-02T08:26:43.000Z","uid":31314,"like":91,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"7030b3d856d71ebf45b7e1990cb39838cf5ab417","tid":764419,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T03:32:36.000Z","msg":"顧客至上是日本人待客之道，東京一間和牛居酒屋最近貼出告示，揚言生啤收費會按客人語氣而定，語氣態度愈差收費愈貴，告示列明若以<span style=\"color: red;\">有禮語氣下單，每杯生啤只收380日圓</span>，即約27港元，但如果<span style=\"color: red;\">態度不好，每杯要收500日圓</span>，即約35港元，如果<span style=\"color: red;\">客人呼喝侍應，每杯更收1000日圓</span>，約70港元。<br />\n<br />\n告示還大字標明：「<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>客人不是上帝，我店的侍應也不是客人的奴隸。</strong></span></span>」居酒屋老闆解釋指，侍應都是兼職大學生，在居酒屋打工是因為有趣，若然每天受惡客閒氣，否則不如去做補習老師。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/aOyCFc_qcCNgKzE8jxbx9A--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NzUwO2g9NjAwO2lsPXBsYW5l/https://media.zenfs.com/creatr-images/GLB/2018-08-02/284869b0-9604-11e8-8a56-4d93e1a4ee56_beer_R.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FaOyCFc_qcCNgKzE8jxbx9A--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NzUwO2g9NjAwO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fcreatr-images%2FGLB%2F2018-08-02%2F284869b0-9604-11e8-8a56-4d93e1a4ee56_beer_R.jpg&h=56524844&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"096e72f435256d7a6ab8c5b273ca1477307c1772","tid":764419,"uid":48006,"like":9,"dislike":19,"score":-10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T03:36:07.000Z","msg":"香港客係大撚晒 <br />\n<br />\n我屌你老母"},{"pid":"77ce706c22666dd923f88e31260a8f10458a51b8","tid":764419,"uid":34409,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T03:40:04.000Z","msg":"土下座叫啤酒係咪免費？"},{"pid":"42c7194230799f8eaaf424ae4bf74dd235d21654","tid":764419,"uid":52605,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T03:54:25.000Z","msg":"耍不耍用敬語叫嘢食?"},{"pid":"7863f68dba9561cc80e47ca4687a6eef1e18d155","ti